{"tid":502932,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋同緊個300萬 Facebook Like 嘅畫家一齊整 Board Game……","createTime":"2017-12-18T11:24:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T07:06:23.000Z","uid":46784,"like":300,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"68f2fdf8ef3bb604ab1313befbb47a0d56e19428","tid":502932,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/18/191253_4379c5e528e82d065e9f86fd6b7e668d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F18%2F191253_4379c5e528e82d065e9f86fd6b7e668d.jpg&h=917a5fea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，有冇人識佢？<br />\n<br />\n利申：其實件事半年前已經傾好，但係拖到今日先話畀大家知，係為咗要有十足把握。因為嚟緊 12月尾我哋就會上台灣嘅集資網-嘖嘖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/18/192244_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F18%2F192244_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg&h=fb181876&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用咗幾長時間諗遊戲規則＆同佢哋傾合作細節，當然唔少得畫畫整片同計劃宣傳。好似好輕描淡寫咁寫完呢一句，但都係成事先敢講出口。香港設計桌上遊戲嘅情況好似一直都不及台灣，可能係因為市場、亦可能因為生活環境<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/18/191512_edab7ba7e203cd7576d1200465194ea8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F18%2F191512_edab7ba7e203cd7576d1200465194ea8.jpg&h=7356116c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到咗今日，我哋希望可以做到啲成績出嚟<br />\n<br />\n好，入正題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/18/191759_90ca01be52b7825448f37f2c4394d707.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F18%2F191759_90ca01be52b7825448f37f2c4394d707.jpg&h=c507c228&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDuncan Run 係一隻考驗大家創意，同熟識朋友/睇穿人心程度嘅遊戲。每個玩家處心積慮就係為咗集齊最好嘅故事籌碼同埋技能，引到你朋友/陌生人會心一笑之餘，又取巧咁獲得最多嘅分數，絕對唔會破壞友誼（？）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/18/192046_44e0cb2843048a72cb10a81af9fdf422.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F18%2F192046_44e0cb2843048a72cb10a81af9fdf422.PNG&h=d884c8c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然，你猜測到嗰個人內心嘅陰暗面你就越著數，科科<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊諗住出一set係俾香港支持者如果過咗某個數目，就會附加入去嘅香港獨有事件、地標卡，大家有冇咩好建議？遲啲我哋收集完意見之後就喺Facebook搞投票！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DuncanRun2018/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDuncanRun2018%2F&d=C05UyVNISS4Wj7JQRWEtmDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=18414384\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DuncanRun2018/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/18/192110_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F18%2F192110_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg&h=6cdcd0e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手填份問卷仲會有機會收到 Duncan Run Board Game 添！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">問卷：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/NtWM3ThLBHBUzcYy1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FNtWM3ThLBHBUzcYy1&d=C05UyVNISS4Wj7JQRWEtmDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=56c58881\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/NtWM3ThLBHBUzcYy1</a></span>"},{"pid":"f80051366c28511338fb2dccb1ab15a6acc46f44","tid":502932,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4021a74524a8b62d384279b134085bc7af36a7d1","tid":502932,"uid":154462,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:35:34.000Z","msg":"留名幫推"},{"pid":"43a9ee4fb2bfb8811cc904e080ff35bf45088cf4","tid":502932,"uid":23549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:36:30.000Z","msg":"點玩架"},{"pid":"2ab930ccbe4ffd4fe1c03bdd5b1d52c7f7cbd19b","tid":502932,"uid":30510,"like":57,"dislike":8,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:37:13.000Z","msg":"科乜撚嘢科呀"},{"pid":"f3d637a525c780836ccc1a81b8d8e240f9538a39","tid":502932,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:39:19.000Z","msg":"即係玩咩先得"},{"pid":"60d1163e9f77326a8c44055417b53299a0ffa0d1","tid":502932,"uid":137088,"like":5,"dislike":31,"score":-26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:39:28.000Z","msg":"畫風不能接受。。。"},{"pid":"26af6aef000f468e5eec3f9e29647fa91c865ad2","tid":502932,"uid":83228,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:40:43.000Z","msg":"完全唔知玩緊咩even上堆fb都0資訊<br />\n之前個世界末日桌遊<br />\n一睇就想玩<br />\n呢個仲乜鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335f7a3694c80807b1383273e4b357ff238a251d","tid":502932,"uid":46784,"like":4,"dislike":22,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:41:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係玩咩先得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n流程一 (準備): <br />\n每位玩家抽取身份卡決定其中一人或三人為裁判(6-8人遊戲 : 3個裁判)。裁判負責審閱其他玩家提供出來的地點卡、時間卡、方式卡、原因卡，功能卡並選出自己心目中覺得最能構成一個有趣故事的卡(3個裁判時採用多數決)。<br />\n<br />\n然後每位玩家輪流從地點卡、時間卡、方式卡、原因卡、功能牌中各抽取三張牌。<br />\n<br />\n流程二(故事發展) : <br />\n此時遊戲開始。首先從地點卡開始，每位玩家把自己心目中覺得最好笑的卡蓋著交給裁判，然後裁判看完所有玩家的卡後選出一張，故事開始發展，被選出的玩家勝利，得到一個分數指示物。之後如此類推，順序為地點卡--&gt;時間卡--&gt;方式卡--&gt;原因卡。<br />\n<br />\n流程三(說故事) :<br />\n裁判需要朗讀一次整個故事。朗讀後玩家需要使出功能卡，裁判需要看完所有玩家的功能卡後選出一張，被選者獲得一個分數指示物。功能卡是一種有著能顛覆整個故事的語句變換牌，玩家可以靠功能牌把整個故事扭轉。<br />\n<br />\n流程四(結算):<br />\n玩家可以自行決定遊玩多少個回合，遊戲完結時統計玩家的分數指示物，擁有最多者為這次遊戲的勝利者。"},{"pid":"1fb5d54df010b4dff332b277e8eaa639d1d1c675","tid":502932,"uid":123461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514dd22105d0d8a5136f2904604ba8731e2521b3","tid":502932,"uid":123461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:48:51.000Z","msg":"正皮等玩"},{"pid":"efde147a089cf666db328eaf32eaa34cb9754c41","tid":502932,"uid":46784,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>科乜撚嘢科呀</blockquote><br />\nsorry,打果時有啲台灣用語無轉番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37db37e6542d5796662df5957fbe64965dde875","tid":502932,"uid":83228,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"錯既地方發生錯既事先好笑<br />\n<br />\n拆開地點㨂好笑<br />\n<br />\n恕我笑點太高跟唔上"},{"pid":"a0c09af442991088fa3de46b25334df2fb63cdf7","tid":502932,"uid":5250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9791cc62f4ae30e18e310809fb39d44470d7b16a","tid":502932,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:51:21.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"01025ff0bccb7c4f1f1a6c0f0e24a797a8a3dc9f","tid":502932,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:51:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錯既地方發生錯既事先好笑<br />\n<br />\n拆開地點㨂好笑<br />\n<br />\n恕我笑點太高跟唔上</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實就係四個地方都有機會係完全9唔搭8，全部由玩家自己揀"},{"pid":"14aefea6bfd495647700c12e149b5f775c23783b","tid":502932,"uid":88029,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:55:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed058014984103a0059657d237c7d46cdef0ab7c","tid":502932,"uid":46784,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朋友結婚, 新娘係我之前sp ，會唔會寫實啲？ <br />\n<br />\n個新郎蝴蝶結，應該填綠色！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地都想，但第一次唔可以去得咁盡，遲啲會同duncan果面傾下整呢啲題材 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82143753f6e3dd8c7a063a913fa30ae533506913","tid":502932,"uid":90680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T12:01:36.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/n